                span Use our scheduler to see what workout to do next based on assigned muscle group to target for that day. Personalize your training schedule to best fit your need.
        .col-sm-6
            img(src='images/duo_tablets.png')#index-section5-image
.row
    #index-section7
        .col-sm-6
            #index-section7-text
